# рџЏ† HolyClub Esports Analytics

Analytics project for HolyClub, a Counter-Strike 2 competitive platform focused on matchmaking, championships, player behavior, anti-cheat signals and operational intelligence.

This project aims to explore and document the HolyClub database structure, build analytical queries and prepare the foundation for future dashboards using SQL, Python and Power BI.

